title: Corinne Fisher: Classy but Trashy
description: Corinne Fisher joins us to talk about eating trashy food, dating a drug dealer, and having yard sales. You may know Corinne Fisher from her podcast, Guys We Fucked, Two Less Lonely Girls, and performing stand up comedy around the country. SUBSCRIBE. RATE. REVIEW.
